Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:05.02,Default,tc,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,750)}面紗下的秘密
